===Conspiracist literature===
* ''[[The Protocols of the Elders of Zion]]''.
* {{cite book |last=Balsiger |first=David W. |first2=Charles E. |last2=Sellier, Jr. |year=1977 |title=[[The Lincoln Conspiracy (book)|The Lincoln Conspiracy]] |location=Los Angeles |publisher=Schick Sun Classic Books |isbn=1-56849-531-5}}
* {{cite book |last=Bryan |first =Gerald B. |coauthors=Talita Paolini, Kenneth Paolini |authorlink =&quot;I AM&quot; Activity |title =Psychic Dictatorship in America |year=2000 |origyear = 1940 |publisher=[[Paolini International|Paolini International LLC]] |isbn=0-9666213-1-X}}
