==Ethnic groups==
[[Image:Hrvatske etnije.gif|thumb|150px|Croatia ethnic map.]]

[[Croatia]] is inhabited mostly by [[Croats]], while [[minority group|minority]] groups include [[Serbs]], [[Bosniaks]], [[Hungarians]], [[Italians]], [[Slovenes]], [[Germans]], [[Czechs]], [[Romani people]] and others. 

